= Ioannis Papapanagiotou Service and Membership

== Academic and Professional Membership

- President (2011-2012) and Vice President (2010-2011) of the ECE NCSU Graduate Student Association 
- Member of IEEE, USENIX and INFORMS
- Voting Member, IEEE Standards Association
- IEEE Technical Committee on Communication Systems Integrations and Modeling
- Technical Chamber of Greece (TEE) - Licensed Professional Engineer in Greece/EU

== Professional Service

=== Chairing and Committees

- Publication chair in IEEE CAMAD 2011
- TPC in IEEE ICCN 2011
- TPC in IEEE GLOBECOM 2009-10
- TPC in IEEE ICC 2010-11
- TPC in IEEE SmartGridComm 2010
- TPC in 3rd, 4th, 5th and 6th IEEE Broadband Wireless Access Workshop, ICC & GLOBECOM 2008-10

TPC: Technical Program Committee 
 
=== Reviewer

IEEE Transactions on Parallel and Distributed Systems, IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications, IEEE Transactions on Communications, IEEE Wireless Communications Magazine, IEEE Communications Surveys and Tutorials, IEEE Communications Letters, ACM Transactions on Modeling and Computer Simulation (TOMACS), Springer Mobile Networks and Applications, Elsevier Computer Communications, EURASIP Journal on Wireless Communications and Networking. Advances in Multimedia Journal - Hindawi Publications, Journal of Zhejiang University Science
